            "product_text_content_2": "<p>Being made from sturdy Nubuck leather, this <a href=\"https://rdxsports.com/4-inch-ipl-uspa-world-powerlifting-congress-approved-powerlifting-leather-gym-belt?acc=15277\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://rdxsports.com/4-inch-ipl-uspa-world-powerlifting-congress-approved-powerlifting-leather-gym-belt?acc=15277\">belt</a> brings great support during intensive drills. The leather itself is rigid and doesn’t stretch or tear under the loads. However, some customers complain about the belt flimsiness because of torn stitching in the first weeks of training.</p><p>Moreover, due to the same width, you’ll get full body support to mitigate bad form and excessive abdominal tension, so you can keep lifting for longer periods without distracting your performance.</p><p>The belt’s high-quality construction ensures its durability: the lining acts as a cushioned padding that strengthens the back, provides comfort, and prevents the belt from digging into the skin. The precise double stitching makes it exceptionally durable.</p>",
