            "product_text_content_1": "<p>Iron Bull is a brand that unites the community of lifters passionate for fitness and weightlifting in particular. The company has immense experience in the sports industry, thus it crafts high-quality and durable pieces of lifting equipment to bring your training to the next level. Even the slogan “Unleash the Beast” tells to uncover the potential in training and push your limits to achieve the next level.</p><p><a href=\"https://ironbullstrength.com/products/premium-10mm-4in-lever-belt?sca_ref=3884196.eg5jxEttuv\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://ironbullstrength.com/products/premium-10mm-4in-lever-belt?sca_ref=3884196.eg5jxEttuv\">This lever belt</a> features a lever buckle that can accommodate various waist sizes by ensuring a secure and adjustable fit. It has double-stitched edges and heavy-duty hardware, so it can withstand any intense workout. The steel lever buckle ensures quick and secure fastening for serious lifters who aim for serious lifting battles.</p><p>The belt is believed to be one of the best powerlifting belts, as it can fit powerlifters, strongmen, and any strength enthusiast performing heavy compound movements. Lifters looking to enhance their core strength will also benefit from using this lever belt while reducing the risk of lower back injury.</p>",
