            "product_text_content_2": "<p>If you participate in any competition, a heavy-duty steel lever buckle will ensure a quick and secure fastening mechanism, so you won't waste time putting the belt on and off between sets.</p><p>The belt’s construction provides the necessary rigidness and support for heavy lifts. The thickness balances comfort and firmness at the same time, allowing lifters to maintain proper posture during squats, deadlifts, and other movements, while its tough design elevates core stability and support during heavy lifts.</p><p>The only drawback of this belt is that it may feel a bit stiff at first, so you have to break it in a bit before it becomes comfortable, although that can occur to any product of this type.</p>",
