            "product_text_content_1": "<p>Started in the USA, the Flexz Fitness company gained a reputation of a top-notch manufacturer who created products built to last.</p><p>It features 10 holes for waist adjustment and ultimate support. Due to the triple stitching, you'll get maximum durability and comfort. <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Flexz-Fitness-Buckle-Powerlifting-Lifting/dp/B01BLHCOB8?tag=wbcmb-20\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.amazon.com/Flexz-Fitness-Buckle-Powerlifting-Lifting/dp/B01BLHCOB8?tag=wbcmb-20\">This lifting belt</a> brings extra strength and support to your back and core, so you can improve your lifts and utilize this lifting accessory for 500-lb deadlifts and squats.</p><p>If you’re a strength athlete just at the start, this belt will satisfy your needs. For a serious powerlifter, the belt offers good support and security needed for heavy lifts.</p><p>The material feels stiff and has an inner black suede lining to improve product wearability. The suede lining is soft and improves the comfort of the belt during lifting sessions. This lever belt comes with double stitching without any loose ends and has uniform width all around. It provides great support all around the core and spine.</p>",
