ers/\">Gifts for Personal Trainers</a></li><li><a href=\"https://blog.warmbody-coldmind.com/guides/what-does-a-weightlifting-belt-do/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://blog.warmbody-coldmind.com/guides/what-does-a-weightlifting-belt-do/\">Key Benefits Of Wearing A Weightlifting Belt</a></li><li><a href=\"https://blog.warmbody-coldmind.com/guides/how-to-wear-a-lifting-belt/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://blog.warmbody-coldmind.com/guides/how-to-wear-a-lifting-belt/\">How to Wear a Lifting Belt</a></li><li><a href=\"https://blog.warmbody-coldmind.com/guides/do-weight-lifting-belts-help-lower-back-pain/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://blog.warmbody-coldmind.com/guides/do-weight-lifting-belts-help-lower-back-pain/\">Do Lifting Belts Help With Back Pain</a></li><li><a href=\"https://blog.warmbody-coldmind.com/guides/types-of-weightlifting-belts/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://blog.warmbody-coldmind.com/guides/types-of-weightlifting-belts/\">Types of Weightlifting Belts</a></li></ul><p>References:</p><ol><li>J. E. Lander, R. L. Simonton, J. K. Giacobbe, “The Effectiveness of Weight Belts during the Squat Exercise,” Medicine & Science in Sports & Exercise 22, no. 1 (1990): 117-126.</li><li>Idsart Kingma, Gert S. Faber, Edin K. Suwarganda, Tom B. M. Bruijnen, Rob J. A. Peters, Jaap H. van Dieën, “Effect of a Stiff Lifting Belt on Spine Compression during Lifting,” Spine 31, no. 22 (2006): E833-E839.</li><li>Margaret J. Rys, Stephan A. Konz, “Lifting Belts: A Review,” International Journal of Occupational Safety and Ergonomics 1, no. 3 (1995): 294-303.</li><li>S. A. Lavender, K. Shakeel, G. B. Andersson, J. S. Thomas, “Effects of a Lifting Belt on Spine Moments and Muscle Recruitments after Unexpected Sudden Loading,” Spine 25, no. 12 (2000): 1569-1578.</li><li>Trevor W. Blanchard, Camille Smith, Sylvain G. Grenier, “In a Dynamic Lifting Task, the Relationship between Cross-Sectional Abdominal Muscle Thickness and the Corresponding Muscle Activity Is Affected